                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I know <persName>Morrison</persName> is right<lb/>\n                                        you'd not obtain a cent <add>?</add> the scoundrel<lb/>\n                                        <add>?</add>, and if you wish to obtain your<lb/> money it\n                                        will have be done, why should<lb/> he go to <placeName><hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\"\n                                                  >Stra<add>?</add>berg</hi></placeName>? and buy an\n                                        estate<lb/> nott you have coming as the\n                                        journa<add>?</add><lb/> take my advise and you I got\n                                        your<lb/> money sue him at once. <persName>Mr<lb/>\n                                                  Morrison</persName> with no justice, if the\n                                        D-<lb/> finds you in earnest, he will pay at once</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(8)\">Yours</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(8)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">S M Isaacs</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p><persName>M Levy</persName> from\n                                                  <sic><placeName>Cincinatti</placeName></sic> is\n                                        engaged<lb/> to a daughter of <persName>John M\n                                                  Davis</persName><lb/> I save two\n                                                  <sic>weedding</sic>\n                                        <date>sunday 2</date><lb/>\n                                        <add>אלה ימי הגבלה</add> and 2 in the <add>לג\n                                        בעומר</add><lb/> is the order of the <add>פרו\n                                        ורבו</add><lb/> day</p>\n                    </body>\n          </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3xw48c60/canvas/p2"
